#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.str.replace.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.str.replace"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:1
msgid "Replace each occurrence of pattern/regex in the Series/Index."
msgstr "替换 Series/Index 中的每个模式/正则表达式匹配项。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:3
msgid ""
"Equivalent to :meth:`str.replace` or :func:`re.sub`, depending on the "
"regex value."
msgstr "等效于 :meth:`str.replace` 或 :func:`re.sub`，取决于 regex 的值。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:6
msgid "String can be a character sequence or regular expression."
msgstr "字符串可以是字符序列或正则表达式。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:8
msgid ""
"Replacement string or a callable. The callable is passed the regex match "
"object and must return a replacement string to be used. See "
":func:`re.sub`."
msgstr ""
"替换字符串或可调用对象。可调用对象接收正则表达式匹配对象，并必须返回要"
"使用的替换字符串。参见 :func:`re.sub`。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:12
msgid "Number of replacements to make from start."
msgstr "从开始位置起要进行的替换次数。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:14
msgid ""
"Determines if replace is case sensitive:  - If True, case sensitive (the "
"default if `pat` is a string) - Set to False for case insensitive - "
"Cannot be set if `pat` is a compiled regex."
msgstr ""
"确定替换是否区分大小写：  - 如果为 True，则区分大小写（当 `pat` 是字符串"
"时的默认值） - 设置为 False 表示不区分大小写 - 如果 `pat` 是编译后的"
"正则表达式，则不能设置此参数。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:14
msgid "Determines if replace is case sensitive:"
msgstr "确定替换是否区分大小写："

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:16
msgid "If True, case sensitive (the default if `pat` is a string)"
msgstr "如果为 True，则区分大小写（当 `pat` 是字符串时的默认值）"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:17
msgid "Set to False for case insensitive"
msgstr "设置为 False 表示不区分大小写"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:18
msgid "Cannot be set if `pat` is a compiled regex."
msgstr "如果 `pat` 是编译后的正则表达式，则不能设置此参数。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:20
msgid ""
"Regex module flags, e.g. re.IGNORECASE. Cannot be set if `pat` is a "
"compiled regex."
msgstr ""
"正则表达式模块标志，例如 re.IGNORECASE。如果 `pat` 是编译后的正则表达式，"
"则不能设置此参数。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:23
msgid ""
"Determines if the passed-in pattern is a regular expression:  - If True, "
"assumes the passed-in pattern is a regular expression. - If False, treats"
" the pattern as a literal string - Cannot be set to False if `pat` is a "
"compiled regex or `repl` is   a callable."
msgstr ""
"确定传入的模式是否为正则表达式：  - 如果为 True，表示传入的模式是"
"正则表达式。 - 如果为 False，则将模式视为字面量字符串 - 如果 `pat` 是编译"
"后的正则表达式或 `repl` 是可调用对象，则不能设为此值。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:23
msgid "Determines if the passed-in pattern is a regular expression:"
msgstr "确定传入的模式是否为正则表达式："

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:25
msgid "If True, assumes the passed-in pattern is a regular expression."
msgstr "如果为 True，表示传入的模式是正则表达式。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:26
msgid "If False, treats the pattern as a literal string"
msgstr "如果为 False，则将模式视为字面量字符串"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:27
msgid ""
"Cannot be set to False if `pat` is a compiled regex or `repl` is a "
"callable."
msgstr "如果 `pat` 是编译后的正则表达式或 `repl` 是可调用对象，则不能设为此值。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:31
msgid ""
"A copy of the object with all matching occurrences of `pat` replaced by "
"`repl`."
msgstr "一个副本对象，其中所有与 `pat` 匹配的内容都被替换为 `repl`。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:35
msgid ""
"* if `regex` is False and `repl` is a callable or `pat` is a compiled"
"       regex     * if `pat` is a compiled regex and `case` or `flags` is "
"set"
msgstr ""
"* 如果 `regex` 为 False 且 `repl` 是可调用对象或者 `pat` 是编译后的"
"正则表达式     * 如果 `pat` 是编译后的正则表达式且设置了 `case` 或 `flags"
"`"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:35
msgid ""
"if `regex` is False and `repl` is a callable or `pat` is a compiled"
"       regex     * if `pat` is a compiled regex and `case` or `flags` is "
"set"
msgstr ""
"如果 `regex` 为 False 且 `repl` 是可调用对象，或者 `pat` 是编译后的"
"正则表达式     * 如果 `pat` 是编译后的正则表达式且设置了 `case` 或 `flags"
"`"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:38
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:39
msgid ""
"When `pat` is a compiled regex, all flags should be included in the "
"compiled regex. Use of `case`, `flags`, or `regex=False` with a compiled "
"regex will raise an error."
msgstr ""
"当 `pat` 是编译后的正则表达式时，所有标志都应包含在该编译后的正则表达式中"
"。使用 `case`、`flags` 或 `regex=False` 与编译后的正则表达式一起使用将会"
"引发错误。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:44
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:45
msgid ""
"When `pat` is a string and `regex` is True, the given `pat` is compiled "
"as a regex. When `repl` is a string, it replaces matching regex patterns "
"as with :meth:`re.sub`. NaN value(s) in the Series are left as is:"
msgstr ""
"当 `pat` 是字符串且 `regex` 为 True 时，给定的 `pat` 会被编译为正则表达式"
"。当 `repl` 是字符串时，它会替换匹配的正则表达式模式，就像使用 :meth:`re."
"sub` 一样。Series 中的 NaN 值保持不变："

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:58
msgid ""
"When `pat` is a string and `regex` is False, every `pat` is replaced with"
" `repl` as with :meth:`str.replace`:"
msgstr ""
"当 `pat` 是字符串且 `regex` 为 False 时，每个 `pat` 都会被替换为 `repl`，"
"就像使用 :meth:`str.replace` 一样："

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:67
msgid ""
"When `repl` is a callable, it is called on every `pat` using "
":func:`re.sub`. The callable should expect one positional argument (a "
"regex object) and return a string."
msgstr ""
"当 `repl` 是可调用对象时，它会在每个 `pat` 上使用 :func:`re.sub` 调用。该"
"可调用对象应该期望一个位置参数（一个正则表达式对象）并返回一个字符串。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:71
msgid "To get the idea:"
msgstr "理解概念："

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:79
msgid "Reverse every lowercase alphabetic word:"
msgstr "反转每个小写字母单词："

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:89
msgid "Using regex groups (extract second group and swap case):"
msgstr "使用正则表达式组（提取第二组并交换大小写）："

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.replace:99
msgid "Using a compiled regex with flags"
msgstr "使用带标志的编译正则表达式"

